ABOUT CHELSEA FOOTBALL CLUB 

Founded in 1905, Chelsea Football Club is an English professional football club based in Fulham, West London with Stamford Bridge as the home of the club. Competing in the Premier League - the top division of English football, the club has had many successes, winning five Premier League titles. The club won their first major honour, the League championship in 1955, followed by the FA Cup in 1970, their first European honour, the Cup Winners' Cup in 1971, and became the third English club to win the Club World Cup in 2022. 

As the Pride of London, Chelsea FC is one of the most successful clubs in terms of overall trophies won. They are the only club to have won all three major European competitions twice and have taken the crown domestically, winning six league titles, eight FA Cups, five League Cups, and four FA Community Shields. Internationally, Chelsea have won the UEFA Champions League, the UEFA Europa League, the UEFA Cup Winners' Cup and the UEFA Super Cup twice each, and the FIFA Club World Cup once since their inception.

The Chelsea YouTube channel provides access to all the build-up, training and behind-the-scenes moments and matchday action along with all the unseen edits and player focus from Reece James, Cole Palmer and Enzo Fernandez to Sam Kerr, Lauren James and many more. It’s the only channel where you’ll get an authentic look at this great club including memorable nights with world-class heroes such as Peter Osgood, Gianfranco Zola, Frank Lampard, John Terry, Didier Drogba & Eden Hazard.

snippet.title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle | MAIN TRAILER
snippet.description:
Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle is only in Movie Theatres September 12 ⚔️ https://demonslayer-movie.com

Tanjiro Kamado – a boy who joined an organization dedicated to hunting down demons called the Demon Slayer Corps after his younger sister Nezuko was turned into a demon.

While growing stronger and deepening his friendships and bonds with fellow corps members, Tanjiro has battled many demons with his comrades, Zenitsu Agatsuma and Inosuke Hashibira. Along the way, his journey has led him to fight alongside the Demon Slayer Corps’ highest-ranking swordsmen, the Hashira, including Flame Hashira Kyojuro Rengoku aboard the Mugen Train, Sound Hashira Tengen Uzui within the Entertainment District, as well as Mist Hashira Muichiro Tokito and Love Hashira Mitsuri Kanroji at the Swordsmith Village.

As the Demon Slayer Corps members and Hashira engaged in a group strength training program, the Hashira Training, in preparation for the forthcoming battle against the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji appears at the Ubuyashiki Mansion. With the head of the Demon Corps in danger, Tanjiro and the Hashira rush to the headquarters but are plunged into a deep descent to a mysterious space by the hands of Muzan Kibutsuji.

The destination of where Tanjiro and Demon Slayer Corps have fallen is the demons’ stronghold – the Infinity Castle. And so, the battleground is set as the final battle between the Demon Slayer Corps and the demons ignites.

Crunchyroll brings you the latest clips, openings, full episodes, and more from your favorite anime!

snippet.title: Can You 100% FNaF World Inside The DEMO?
snippet.description:
FNaF World is one of my favorite free games ever made, but unfortunately my bank account is in the negative so I can’t afford anything free anymore. I went to Vegas last month and bet my entire savings account (and then some!) on black, thinking my YouTuber luck would carry over. Spoiler alert, it didn’t. Thankfully, I can still play the FNaF World Demo even though I’m in debt, so here I am trying to figure out a way to make content out of it. I guess I haven’t made the obligatory 100%ing FNaF World video yet like everyone else, so now I’ve decided to try and 100% the game with the added twist of doing it inside of the FNaF World Demo. This seems a lot simpler than it truly was however, as many literal barriers are found within the world halting your progress, and you can’t even use most of the characters! I would say if this video does well I can pay off my debts, but I actually think I already have in the process of making this! I think my terrible luck with pokemon cards finally decided to go away, as the other day I opened a booster bundle of Prismatic Evolutions and pulled a beautiful Eevee EX SIR, which is worth about 140 dollars. I haven’t really told any of my friends that I pulled the card though, so if you’re reading this I guess you’ve got some elite TheDapperWaffle knowledge to totally impress your friends! By the way if you even bothered to look at this description, write the comment “I am quite fond of DeeDee’s fishing hole” so I know you’re a real one, thanks!

2:16 - Chapter 1 (I’m Gonna Play UCN!)
4:05 - Chapter 2 (ok let’s start for real :))

15:26 - Chapter 5 (CBT)

snippet.title: The American Hotel Is Finally Back...After 5 Years
snippet.description:
It's done! The American Hotel stands once again after 5 years of long days and longer nights. This is a moment I've literally dreamed of for years now and to see it in front of me is very exciting!

Thank you all for supporting this journey and helping make this possible. To the people viewing at home, the visitors who came for a day, or the volunteers who shared blood sweat and tears. We did it. Against all odds, the American Hotel is back. And I can't WAIT to see what comes next. 

More photos of the journey: https://www.instagram.com/brentwunderwood/

snippet.title: Ultimate Nerf Gun Battle w/ Zach King!
snippet.description:
Welcome to the fourth week of Camp CrunchLabs! This week Zach King joins us for the ultimate nerf battle! It's not too late to join Camp CrunchLabs! Join here: http://www.campcrunchlabs.com 

Each build-it-yourself STEM toy teaches the magic and fun in engineering principles and coincides with exclusive weekly videos like this one that accelerate your learning! Ready for Camp? Visit http://www.campcrunchlabs.com for more info.

A big thanks to our special guest​⁠ @ZachKing for joining me on Jupiter! And @outofdarts for an epic build. 

Week 2 Super Challenge Montage:
https://youtu.be/6xcJcHQPpf8

This weeks Challenge:
CREATE A MINIATURE WORLD

Ever been to a museum and seen big displays of life in miniature? Now it's time to create your own! Make a miniature world and build your own diorama! Build a tiny model of your house, your dream bedroom, or invent a new planet! Use Legos, action figures, or just create your own characters from cardboard. Find ways to challenge yourself and take it to the next level of creativity, imagination, and even your sense of humor if you can! Craft a story around this tiny world in your diorama and document it by taking a picture or give us a quick video tour.

As always, be safe and get a parent's permission before building. Once you've filmed it, work with your parents to share it with us!

HOW TO SUBMIT YOUR CHALLENGES?
Parents: Tag challenge project video submissions @crunchlabs with #CampCrunchlabsContest on Instagram, X, TikTok or Facebook. Then complete this form https://www.crunchlabs.com/pages/camp-planet-page-jupiter


NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Contest begins at 9:00 a.m. PT on 6/7/25 & ends 11:59 p.m. PT on 7/23/25; but, to be eligible to win Grand Prize, one must enter by 11:59 p.m. PT on 7/8/25. Open to legal residents of the 50 U.S. & D.C., who are 18+ and the parent or legal guardian of at least (1) child between 8-16 years of age. Grand Prize winner must travel 7/20/25-7/22/25. See Official Rules for full details including entry periods, entry requirements, prize descriptions and judging criteria. Void where prohibited.
Full rules: http://crunchlabs.com/camp-rules
